messages.msgSnippet: This is the beginning of the reminder of the upcoming conference: 1) I just wanted to remind those of you who have never been to the Live and Learn Conferences
messages.messageBody:
This is the beginning of the reminder of the upcoming conference:
1)
I just wanted to remind those of you who have never been to the Live and

Learn Conferences (and those of you who may have forgoten!) to bring a
sweater.
Hotels can be quite chilly, and the conference room's temperature is
hard to
control.

[] This conference by title sounds very interesting but I have never
heard of it. I am obviously in the dark up here on Vancouver Island,
BC, Canada. When is it? Where is it? What is the website as I presume
there is one?
Thanks
Susan
